# Operator deploy runbooks — kept private (they name the box's SSH user/IPs and
# the RMIT production DB host + login). Operational templates with placeholders
# only (deploy/deploy.sh, bitbalance.service, ngrok.yml) stay tracked.
/DEPLOY.md
/deploy/DEPLOY-CachyOS.md

# Keep docs ignored by default, but allow the architecture contract.
docs/*
